  that is now shared with Debian and Mandriva.
- Add smilutils-gcc4.4.patch to fix build with gcc 4.4. Thanks
  Mandriva!
- Drop kino-1.1.0-playlistsupport.diff: fixed upstream.
- Use makeinstall macro.

